<content>
    <para id="id2426578">10. The Trailer Park - <link url="http://www.movie-trailers.com/Main/main.html"><emphasis effect="bold">http://www.movie-trailers.com/Main/main.html</emphasis></link>A vast archive of old and new movie trailers.</para>
    <para id="id6846385">11. TV Party - <link url="http://www.tvparty.com/"><emphasis effect="bold">http://www.tvparty.com/</emphasis></link> A nostalgic tribute to the great and not-so-great TV shows, commercials and promotions of yesteryear.</para>
    <para id="id1163975240819">12. TV To Me -<link url="http://www.tvtome.com/"><emphasis effect="bold">http://www.tvtome.com/</emphasis></link> A valuable source of information on TV shows past, present and in development.</para>
    <para id="id1163978399695">13. Without a box - <link url="http://www.withoutabox.com/"><emphasis effect="bold">http://www.withoutabox.com</emphasis></link> A resource for filmmakers submitting their films to festivals; also has a deep list of other filmmakers' services.</para>
    <para id="id1163985222292">14. Final Draft - <link url="http://www.finaldraft.com/"><emphasis effect="bold">http://www.finaldraft.com/</emphasis></link> This is the homepage for Final Draft, the screenwriting software that we will be using in this class.</para>
    <para id="id1163987193567">15. Wordplay "Points for Style" - <link url="http://www.wordplayer.com/columns/wp23.Points.for.Style.html"><emphasis effect="bold">http://www.wordplayer.com/columns/wp23.Points.for.Style.html</emphasis></link> Contains some useful tips on writing screenplays.</para>
